snippet: The Israeli military said it struck a plant for weapons manufacturing, a weapons storage site and what it called a “terror activity site.”
abstract: Israeli warplanes carry out raids against three Palestinian targets in Gaza, soon after militants fired a rocket from Gaza into southern Israel.

headline.main: Israeli Military Strikes Targets in Gaza
